{"tid":1575922,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"鷹頭獅 = 獅鳥 = 勇武神獸","createTime":"2019-09-17T04:25:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-17T04:34:16.000Z","uid":274964,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"104653ec19b845b3bd87237d1f697a9c8d9eb5dc","tid":1575922,"uid":274964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T04:25:49.000Z","msg":"林夕係預言家!<br />\n<br />\n點解鷹頭獅(獅鳥)係全黑?<br />\n點解公安武警要穿上裝甲扮警察?<br />\n過去盜亦有盜，現在專打大肚婆細路。<br />\n土匪係咪講緊鄉黑?<br />\n荃灣的兄弟被斬血脈噴泉。<br />\n獅鳥要冷面，要鐵石心腸<br />\n要穿上裝甲<br />\n要維護公正為人護法<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n未來警察<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n曲：羅大佑　詞：林夕　唱：太極樂隊<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警匪每天比武　當槍戰也枯燥<br />\n<br />\n公安武警穿上裝甲當戰袍<br />\n<br />\n過去盜亦有道　到了明日制度<br />\n<br />\n放棄人道要用機器捉拿強盜<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n黑手永斬不斷　不必電腦推算<br />\n<br />\n土匪劫匪暴徒罪人兇手捉不完<br />\n<br />\n冷血強盜作亂　當血脈是噴泉<br />\n<br />\n要靠同樣冷面警察不會手軟<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有賊便有警察在穿插　未來全是鐵石做那心腸<br />\n<br />\n要維護公正只好要用盔甲　未來警察今天要出發<br />\n<br />\n有賊便有警察在穿插　未來全是鐵石做那心腸<br />\n<br />\n要維護公正只好要用盔甲　未來警察今天要出發<br />\n<br />\n未來警察為人民護法<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cYAx4Bs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcYAx4Bs.png&h=0a04fc34&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3640ec0ed31e31979fe6c0277283df68368d4d40","tid":1575922,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T04:26:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yt2HG33.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyt2HG33.jpg&h=9fcb0aae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TrPZKfU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTrPZKfU.jpg&h=433e1fe6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3f3f9d2916a057e05b46b8881de717ea771f80b4","tid":1575922,"uid":38191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T04:34:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}